name: HeavenOrangeMix
description:
This model is a simple merge of 60% Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix and 40% Abyss Orange Mix 3. Full credit goes to their respective creators.

This is perfect for people who like the anime style, but would also like to tap into the advanced lighting and lewdness of AOM3, without struggling with the softer look.

There is also a separate Vtubers version, great for Hololive and to a lesser extent Nijisanji and independent vtubers. This is not the default version as it doesn't play as nicely with Loras (but there are some examples anyway).

This model is also available on tensor.art
